last_episode_to_air.name: No Surrender
last_episode_to_air.overview: Thord tries to tow out a car that crashed sixty metres into a field after a snowstorm, but gets stressed when a winch failure threatens the rescue.

name: Ice Road Rescue

next_episode_to_air.name: Causing Chaos
next_episode_to_air.overview: When a truck driver slides to a standstill on ice, but refuses help from Thord, he creates chaos on the main road.

overview: Reality series following a group of truck drivers in the mountain passes of Norway, some of the most dangerous roads in all of Europe.

seasons.name: Season 6
seasons.overview: Arctic storms produce the lowest temperatures in ten years. But the heroes of the winter road can not be stopped by minus 30 degrees, and they risk their lives to save drivers in need. Thord and Bjørn face unexpected threats and old rivals. In Overhalla, Jo Roger returns from injury, and he wants to show that he is still the king of the north.

episodes.name: Feast or Famine
episodes.overview: In Odda, the biggest snowfall that local truck towers Thord Paulsen and Olav Eike have ever seen sets in, creating chaos on the roads.

episodes.name: Crazy People
episodes.overview: In Hardanger, two smugglers have driven into a snowbank, and towing veteran Bjørn Lægreid can hardly believe what's inside their vehicle.

episodes.name: Fire and Ice
episodes.overview: In Voss, a fish truck has gone off the road, and it's up to Ove and his crew to get it back up before the valuable fish goes bad.

episodes.name: Beggars Can't be Chooser
episodes.overview: Thord Paulsen and Bjørn Lægreid rescue a sunken boat in the fjord, while Frank Sebulonsen assists a German truck driver transporting nine cars.

episodes.name: Black Ice
episodes.overview: In the south, Bjørn Lægreid fixes a snowplough and gives a ride to a minister, while in the north, Jo Roger Blengsli slips off the road.

episodes.name: Into the Woods
episodes.overview: In the north a harvester has tipped over, and an excavator is about to sink into a mud hole.

episodes.name: Stuck Trucks
episodes.overview: Bjørn Lægreid heads out into the storm to help a truck and clear the road for the ploughers, but ends up stuck himself and unable to help.

episodes.name: The Night Shift
episodes.overview: Thord has to keep the road open during heavy snowfall. Bjørn is on the mountain rescuing a truck, when a car tries to bypass him and gets stuck.

episodes.name: Fishy Business
episodes.overview: Bjørn helps a car whose fuel has frozen before the road is forced to close. Thord works tirelessly to keep the trucks moving and the road open.

episodes.name: Extreme Rescues
episodes.overview: Thord, Bjørn and the guys get together to take a look back on the season and ponder a video recording of a rescue mission going horribly wrong.

episodes.name: Danger On Death Hill
episodes.overview: Bjørn helps an inexperienced foreign driver, while Kristoffer and Erik battle challenging conditions to rescue a trailer in rush hour traffic

episodes.name: Big Freeze
episodes.overview: Thord and rookie rescue worker Andrzej have their work cut out for them when they help a Polish driver with valuable cargo loaded with sugar.

episodes.name: Ferry Go Round
episodes.overview: Thord is faced with an extremely challenging rescue that leaves the whole community locked in, unable to get in or out of the main road blocked by the huge eight-wheel- trailer. In the North Kristoffer is left with a dirty job, literally speaking. A garbage truck has overturned due to the slippery roads.

episodes.name: Crime Scene Rescue
episodes.overview: Thord becomes part of a crime scene investigation, rookie Andrej is faced with an overloaded car, and Bjørn keeps the big mountains of Norway safe.

episodes.name: Winter Woes
episodes.overview: Thord is called out to rescue a trailer and prevent it flooding the roads with its milky cargo. Lone wolf Bjørn has a bad day.

episodes.name: Storm Chaos Mountain
episodes.overview: The biggest storm in years is about to hit Norway and all the rescue workers have their work cut out.

episodes.name: Military Mayhem
episodes.overview: Bjørn is caught up in a high speed chase and car theft investigation: A "Bonnie and Clyde" of the mountains have stolen three cars and are on the run.

episodes.name: Edge Of Disaster
episodes.overview: It takes a special breed of men to pull off the perfect 'Ice Road Rescue'...from a driver smuggling nappies out of Norway, to a truck in trouble full of fresh fish!

episodes.name: Deadly Drops
episodes.overview: Thord has his work cut out unravelling roads thrown into chaos by a driver who’s abandoned his stuck truck and gone missing. Bjorn thinks he’ll have a pleasant day out rescuing an old friend but learns that, in the mountains of Norway, beauty comes laced with deadly danger. And rookie Kristoffer gambles his fresh reputation with a fishy cargo rescue that could turn rotten...

episodes.name: Winter's End
episodes.overview: The toughest months of another brutal winter are over. The ice road rescue guys might be business rivals, but they're also firm friends. They head to the mountains for some R&R, and to relive the rescues that made this season the most dramatic and daring ever.

episodes.name: River Deep
episodes.overview: The team risk it all to keep Norway's most treacherous roads open. But if anything is damaged during a rescue, they could find themselves facing a crippling bill.

episodes.name: Mean Machine
episodes.overview: The ice road rescuers spring into action when a 30-tonne excavator upends itself in a deep ditch in the South of Norway.

episodes.name: Edge of Disaster
episodes.overview: Tow truck boss Thord and his team tackle the biggest rescue of their season when a 40-tonne snow plough crashes down a bank and on to a frozen lake.

episodes.name: Freak Weather
episodes.overview: The tow truckers get a new enemy - Mother Nature - as sudden changes in temperatures throw up unforeseen challenges for the ice road rescuers.

episodes.name: Let It Snow
episodes.overview: It's Thord to the rescue when a storm slides a 20-ton transporter off the road and lands a car in a ditch. A driver's rookie error riles Bjorn on the mountain pass.

episodes.name: Chains Of Chaos
episodes.overview: Bjord struggles to control his anger when a reckless move throws a trucker into a danger. Thord heads out to rescue a driver who made a similarly risky error.

episodes.name: Toxic Cargo
episodes.overview: Junior tow trucker Ole heads off on a major solo mission. Thor goes to the rescue of a carpenter, only to find he's not equipped for the task.

episodes.name: Fish Frenzy
episodes.overview: Boss Thord calls on his old mate Bjorn when a fish trailer needs urgent help. In the north, the team bring in the heavy machinery when a huge lorry overturns.

episodes.name: In the Woods
episodes.overview: Thord gets a blast from the past when he goes to the rescue of his old driving instructor. Jo springs into action when a truck gets stuck deep in the forest.

episodes.name: The Gallows
episodes.overview: A blizzard hits the mountains sending an injured Bjorn out on a risky mission. Thord throws caution to the wind when the notorious Gallows claim a new victim.

episodes.name: Captain Chaos
episodes.overview: As the tough winter season comes to an end, Thord contemplates a new beginning as he meets up with a rival to discuss a potential expansion.

episodes.name: Who's Boss?
episodes.overview: Thord and Bjoern join forces, and 23-year-old Ole Henrik is temporarily in charge.

episodes.name: Rookie Challenge
episodes.overview: Acting boss Ole Henrik puts his rookie crew to the test on its first solo rescue.

episodes.name: Risk On The Rocks
episodes.overview: Boss Thord puts his life on the line to rescue a 20-ton bread truck stuck on rocks.

episodes.name: Landslide Lottery
episodes.overview: Thord hurries to save a 50-ton truck and trailer that threatens to start a landslide.

episodes.name: Black Ice Battle
episodes.overview: When a truck driver won't pay for his rescue, Thord threatens him with house arrest.

episodes.name: Gridlock Hazard
episodes.overview: When Thord rescues a truck stuck on ice, impatient drivers put lives in danger.

episodes.name: Moonlight Mayhem
episodes.overview: Time is short and the police pile on the pressure when Thord struggles to get a 16-wheeler back on the road.

episodes.name: Tough at the Top
episodes.overview: A drill rig hangs over a 15 metre cliff and Ole Henrik must make a life-threatening decision.

episodes.name: Troubled Times
episodes.overview: Arctic storms produce the lowest temperatures in ten years. But the heroes of the winter road can not be stopped by minus 30 degrees, and they risk their lives to save drivers in need. Thord and Bjørn face unexpected threats and old rivals. In Overhalla, Jo Roger returns from injury, and he wants to show that he is still the king of the north.

episodes.name: Rivals on the Brink
episodes.overview: Bjorn joins forces with a rival company to rescue a truck that crashed into a cliff face, and Thord struggles to get a flipped tractor back on its wheels

episodes.name: Deadline Danger
episodes.overview: When an Arctic storm kicks off the coldest winter of a decade, Thord tries to rescue a truck blocking a blind bend but the driver ignores Thord’s instructions and puts all their lives at risk. A blizzard causes chaos for Bjorn when a jackknifed truck blocks the road. And in the far north, a truck full of fish on a tight deadline crashes into a snowbank so rescue boss Jo Roger has to get it back on track.

episodes.name: Blizzard Battle
episodes.overview: To protect their business, Thord and Bjoern open a new garage on the Hardangervidda mountain. Bjoern heads out to rescue a truck causing chaos, but the driver has Bjoern losing his temper, and almost his fingers. When Ole Henrik tries to save a jackknifed truck and trailer, a reckless manoeuvre gets him in trouble. Now the young tow trucker needs to be rescued himself.

episodes.name: Pressure Pile-Up
episodes.overview: The police put Thord under pressure to rescue a truck blocking a tunnel on the express route. Bjoern rescues a truck that’s slid out on sheet ice - but faces danger when passing trucks come too close for comfort. In the far north, a flying winch wire threatens Jo Roger and Ole Henrik when they try to rescue a crashed out truck.

episodes.name: Big Boss Battle
episodes.overview: Thord’s under stress when a rescue fails at his third attempt and time is running out. Bjoern tries to get a 46-ton truck and trailer out of a deep ditch, but the only thing that’s moving is his own tow truck. In the far North, Jo Roger’s on a mission to get a truck and trailer that tipped over back onto its wheels. The truck’s on a tight deadline delivering fresh salmon for export so he has to hurry to save the day.

episodes.name: White Out Warriors
episodes.overview: Thord must battle the biggest blizzard of the winter rescuing a truck carrying massive iron pipes, and Tor Steinar risks frostbite to recover a truck and trailer with frozen brakes. Jo Roger tries to save a thirty-five ton excavator that slid down a steep bank, but the extreme cold causes equipment failure - and when brittle steel snaps, lives are at risk.

episodes.name: High Roads, High Stakes
episodes.overview: Thord’s under stress when a rescue fails at his third attempt and time is running out. Bjoern tries to get a 46-ton truck and trailer out of a deep ditch, but the only thing that’s moving is his own tow truck. In the far North, Jo Roger’s on a mission to get a truck and trailer that tipped over back onto its wheels. The truck’s on a tight deadline delivering fresh salmon for export so he has to hurry to save the day.

6.name: Season 6
6.overview: Arctic storms produce the lowest temperatures in ten years. But the heroes of the winter road can not be stopped by minus 30 degrees, and they risk their lives to save drivers in need. Thord and Bjørn face unexpected threats and old rivals. In Overhalla, Jo Roger returns from injury, and he wants to show that he is still the king of the north.

episodes.name: Marathon Mission
episodes.overview: Thord and Bjoern are tested to the limits when they have to rescue a truck from falling into a lake.

episodes.name: Test of Mettle
episodes.overview: Thord and Bjoern battle one of Norway’s biggest storms in a decade as they try to rescue a truck loaded with steel girders.

episodes.name: Roadblock Emergency
episodes.overview: Bjoern is put under pressure when a head-on collision between two trucks blocks an ambulance on an emergency call-out.

episodes.name: Absolute Destruction
episodes.overview: Thord and Bjoern face the ultimate rescue challenge when a truck is destroyed after crashing 40 metres down a mountainside.

episodes.name: Blizzard Showdown
episodes.overview: When a mountain blizzard causes a double accident, Bjoern is forced to call his rivals for help

episodes.name: Triple Jeopardy
episodes.overview: Jo Roger’s rookies are put to the test with a triple rescue, but the mission gets off to a rocky start when their most powerful truck gets stuck.

episodes.name: Winter’s Payback
episodes.overview: Thord and Andrzej fall prey to the Norwegian winter and, in a shocking twist of events, they end up in need of rescue!

episodes.name: Police Holdup
episodes.overview: Thord and Bjoern face a roadside standoff with the Police when they’re forced to stop a rescue in its tracks.

episodes.name: Off-Road Roulette
episodes.overview: Racing to a rescue, rookie Terjes in big trouble when he crashes Thords tow-truck.

episodes.name: Head Into Danger
episodes.overview: When a truck crashes into a snowbank in the mountains, Thord and rookie Terje must put their lives at risk to save its valuable cargo.

episodes.name: Overload
episodes.overview: When theres chaos in the mountains and the emergency calls just keep coming, Thords running out of options.

episodes.name: River Rescue
episodes.overview: Jo Roger and Ole Henrik struggle to rescue a trailer load of salt that threatens to pollute Norway’s biggest salmon river. Any slip-up could cause an environmental disaster.

episodes.name: All Nighter
episodes.overview: When a truck smashes into a barrier, Third and Bjoern work into the small hours to save its cargo. Jo is called out if his bed to rescue a truck buried in snow.

episodes.name: Road Closed!
episodes.overview: Born and Thord rescue a truck that got stuck just 200 metres from its destination. Jo tries to save a harvester, but then it’s impatient driver endangers his crew.

episodes.name: Narrow Escape
episodes.overview: Thord risks getting crushed when a runaway trailer threatens a main road. Terje’s simple rescue gets complicated and Torsten and Isaac help a truck that’s overturned.

episodes.name: Sink or Swim
episodes.overview: Born risks everything to rescue a tractor. Thord gets stuck in the mud while helping a truck and when a winch wire slips, Jo fears disaster.

episodes.name: Wild Ride
episodes.overview: A tricky rescue of an excavator forces Thord to find extraordinary solutions, but hes in double trouble when rookie Terje messes up.

episodes.name: A Night of Havoc
episodes.overview: When a salmon truck crashes into a ditch, it kicks off a night of havoc for Thord. With truck drivers in trouble all over his territory, Thords team is pushed to the limit.

episodes.name: Convoy Carnage
episodes.overview: When wild weather and traffic convoys cause carnage, Thord races against time to rescue stranded drivers.

episodes.name: Danger Zone
episodes.overview: Thord pits his life against speeding traffic to rescue a stranded forty-ton truck that threatens to slide back into oncoming traffic.

episodes.name: Spooky Night
episodes.overview: In the dead of night, Thord and Erlend get spooked, trying to rescue a van that crashed beside a graveyard.

episodes.name: No Surrender
episodes.overview: Thord tries to tow out a car that crashed sixty metres into a field after a snowstorm, but gets stressed when a winch failure threatens the rescue.

episodes.name: Causing Chaos
episodes.overview: When a truck driver slides to a standstill on ice, but refuses help from Thord, he creates chaos on the main road.

episodes.name: Double Trouble
episodes.overview: When Thord and Bjoern rescue a truck that threatens to tip, Thord crawls beneath the trailer during the pull, putting his life in Bjoerns hands.
